1001542.1000851.1000867.1000975.title=TRD 16" Alloy and Tires 1001542.1000851.1000867.1000971.description=Give your Tacoma the look! These TRD race-inspired alloy wheels incorporate rugged off-road styling, blended with just the right amount of street flare, to boost Tacoma's bold appearance:
•Satin silver spokes with a spun aluminum center cap and bright-machined lip for a distinct look
•Alloy wheels are lighter and provide better heat dissipation than comparable steel wheels
•Incorporates the proper weight, offset and brake clearance to ensure proper fit, finish and reliability

16-in. performance tires are often expected to experience greater tire wear than conventional tires.
